Universal Product Code (UPC) Calculator
-----------------------
This Calculator will take a 6-digit product code
and generate a trailing 7th check digit to produce
the final 7 digit UPC
Please Enter 6 digit code
411451
The 7 digit final UPC is : 4114514
Press any key to continue...

